perl -pi -e 's,-flat_namespace -undefined suppress,,g' configure
If that fails, maybe try to add '-lfoo' to Makefile.in
Or, if that fails too,  change '-undefined suppress -flat_namespace' 
to '-undefined dynamic_lookup'

